title: Install GNOME Customizations
note: ⚠️ Only if you are using **GNOME** and your distro is missing this stuff.
step: Install `gnome-tweaks` and `gnome-shell-extension-manager`
bash:
sudo apt install -y gnome-tweaks gnome-shell-extension-manager
step: Restore Dock Features (only required on some distros)
item: [Dash To Dock](https://extensions.gnome.org/)
item: [Tray Icons](https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/615/appindicator-support)
