title: Install uv tool installer and Python manager
note: Everyone needs this! It's how I manage Python and Various Apps
step: Download & run installer
bash:
curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh
step: Ensure uv is on PATH for this session
bash:
export PATH="$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH"

